The paper discusses the vulnerability of neural networks to adversarial examples and proposes a defense mechanism. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer security and cryptography (cs.CR), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
